{
  "stem": "24346.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And these people were never heard of.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These were the people that supplied the clothes-- what I mentioned, we select a shirt, shirt-- that was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There came a time in 1942 where they needed, not 10,000, 15,000.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They wanted 50,000, 60,000.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, I can't give you that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My resorts will be empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wouldn't have workers, who, to produce stuff for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They said, if you wouldn't, we'll come in and take it ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They called it [? the schpera, ?] like, you are to stay home, so you cannot go out in the street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they came in, the Germans, in the ghetto, and the Jewish Police worked with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They encircled a square block of houses, and said, everybody out, whoever is going to remain home is going to be shot on the spot, so better everybody go down to the street.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We went down to the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We're gathered in a big place in the street, And they had set up lines that narrowed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The crowd was standing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to walk till we narrowed like cattle, came, like, individually, we had to go through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was a guy, maybe it was [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Mengele ?] from Auschwitz, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know the man, so I can't say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was one guy who looked at the face, and was selection-- one to this side, one to this side, just like your heard the selections from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That was quite a few times, and they took out many people from the ghetto, and they were never heard of.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Their clothes-- because people recognized some of the clothes that came back-- was from their neighbors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "These are two incidents I wanted to mention.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister was taken out before, my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
